The ten times i started the game it started giving me 11 warnings (yellow)for all ten starts   , at first the game said it was the B9partswitch with all 11 warning  .
   Now i'm not getting that warning ,but still shows 11warnings when it loads the cache at the start of the game .    My question ..Where or how do i find exactly where these warnings are and how can i fix them ?
Either copy the text of the warnings or (better still) upload your KSP.log somewhere and provide a link. It could be a bad patch or something trying to add undefined resources to a tank.
